{"tid":510550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實好多窮人都唔明，生仔除左累左下一代，最緊要累埋自己","createTime":"2017-12-26T15:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T17:36:31.000Z","uid":58316,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d9af546fa731eb5ef616e398a65ab224d73ac3","tid":510550,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"好似新起公屋個班唔鹹唔淡住客<br />\n或者住劏房個d<br />\n其實點解要生仔有咩得着<br />\n話咩累左下一代呢d唔講講到尋<br />\n最緊要係累埋自己<br />\n而家個社會你窮基本上冇得翻身<br />\n但窮極揾份萬頭工<br />\n同老豆老母住又好<br />\n揾人合租又好<br />\n你唔生細路生活係香港地人生都唔會太難過<br />\n食乜有乜<br />\n社會相對自由<br />\n一部電腦電話提供大部份娛樂<br />\n機舖卡拉ok club馬會冒險樂園商場食肆aia美食節<br />\n三間電視台睇到你唔睇<br />\n行山滑水健身遙控車滑翔傘<br />\n日本韓國台灣曼谷芭堤雅布吉<br />\n世上咁多野玩玩三百年都玩唔哂<br />\n而家唔係叫你玩車玩錶hifi呢d奢侈野<br />\n就算去旅行通街平機票窮人都afford到<br />\n但窮人一生仔人生既唯一意義就等於無了期揾食養家揾食養家揾食養家<br />\n明明有條易行d既路點解偏要&hellip;&hellip;挑戰自己？"},{"pid":"bd7b7bbcf9bc601bc37c29b3851b374e2f9efe8b","tid":510550,"uid":55533,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"大腦俾條短撚控制左係咁<br />\n因果報應黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a1f3823d47678d89de848e3688e4c9da99579f","tid":510550,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:22:18.000Z","msg":"咁你會唔會自己了斷自己?"},{"pid":"1fa85ffe60dc495d99e55bc5497491b1e45452ce","tid":510550,"uid":65144,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:25:18.000Z","msg":"兩公婆月薪加埋冇5萬以上真係唔好生<br />\n<br />\n窮人覺得下一代可以上到位幫到自己脫貧呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5cb0fabef6a5c31ad395f16ea0a54257fc2ca3","tid":510550,"uid":89931,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇計呀 班傻仔以為生咗個仔出嚟就可以 光宗耀祖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e555ecaf8fff25a5e6c1478e5aa17c1b143f1c","tid":510550,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"頭大無腦<br />\n可能個頭大過條撚<br />\n所以用下體思考<br />\n呢個時候敬請安全移除下體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fe3d3b447a1276ee1e04564f45352c847f8373","tid":510550,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a5cb0fabef6a5c31ad395f16ea0a54257fc2ca3","tid":510550,"uid":89931,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"冇計呀 班傻仔以為生咗個仔出嚟就可以 光宗耀祖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"2017了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603f6d64842e06ed90312117c2beabb05db34c45","tid":510550,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e7acc630d935e1f0d34a1c2bad172d8a6c82b89","tid":510550,"uid":79353,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"603f6d64842e06ed90312117c2beabb05db34c45","tid":510550,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有錢買野玩仲安慰"},{"pid":"55bda47cc3f52254fe0c9d3e45577197452988e2","tid":510550,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"如果每次避孕都中咁果啲人點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8e8acf16f054e394b379618592b3fa8fc24c17","tid":510550,"uid":74858,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"有咁醒就唔駛窮啦<br />\n好多窮人尤其上一代衰在冇遠見<br />\n係又生唔係又生諗住挨到個仔女大就得<br />\n咁跟住呢? 錢佢後生又儲唔到 仔女又養唔起佢<br />\n最後咪臨到唔過得世做隻廢老妹下妹下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d